<!-- GETTING STARTED -->
## Getting Started

This is travel app project

### Prerequisites

* Docker desktop
* Android Studio
* IntelliJ IDEA




### Installation
1. Clone the repo
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/kyozun/flutter_and_spring_boot_final
   ```
2. Run docker-compose to setup database
   ```sh
   docker compose up -d
   ```

3. Open Spring Boot Folder and Run
    ```sh
    mvn spring-boot:run
   ```
4. Open Flutter Folder and Run
     ```sh
   flutter run -v
   ```
